	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_1_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>A rebellious Great Person swears loyalty to {3_PlayerName}!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_2_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>A nomadic branch of the Bulgarian people return home after a thousand years.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_3_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName}'s Writers are experiencing a religious awakening!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_4_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>A Bulgarian Order of Merit has been founded for {3_PlayerName} to reward loyal soldiers!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_5_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>Agrarians have siezed political power in Bulgaria!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_6_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>An aggressive, militarist spirit has captured the Bulgarian spirit. Men and women everywhere are ready to fight and die in {3_PlayerName}'s total war!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>The Rampant Lion</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_HELP">
			<Text>My Lord, a messanger from the frontier! A fire rises in the countryside and is heading towards the Capital.[NEWLINE]We must be prepared when the crisis begins!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Receive a Great Person of your choice.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Await the arrival of what remains of the horde.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Provide {1_YieldCost} worth of training to your Writers, who now yield an additional +2 [ICON_PEACE] Faith.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Celebrate the martial prowess of the Bulgarian people with {1_YieldCost}. Melee, Gun and Mounted Units gain the Order Of Merit Promotion.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>Allow an Agrarian ideological movement to come into power. Your [ICON_GREAT_SCIENTIST] Scientists, [ICON_GREAT_MERCHANT] Merchants and [ICON_GREAT_ENGINEER] Engineers lose -2 of the primary yield. Farms generate +1 [ICON_FOOD] Food and +1 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_HELP_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>For the next {4_Turns} all your Cities experience [COLOR_POSITIVE_TEXT]WLTKD[ENDCOLOR]. Eligible Units, as well as those trained in the next {4_Turns} receive the March Promotion.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>*A Great Person has rallied the smallfolk to his cause and are on their way to challenge your rule!*[NEWLINE]I did not become the greatest ruler in history without mastering the art of political manipulation. Let them come. They will leave as agents of the throne!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*An old offshoot of the Bulgarian people has returned home after all these years. But do they come as friends, or as conquerors?*[NEWLINE]We shall find out soon enough. Ready the city guard.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*A religious movement has taken hold in the far reaches of the Empire*[NEWLINE]These holy men should be welcomed. We shall put them to work copying and discussing our sacred texts.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*A batallion of the military have gone rogue, angry at what the perceive is the erosion of Bulgarian beliefs*[NEWLINE]Their beliefs are my beliefs, if there is some presumed slight them, we can discuss some course of resolve.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>*The peasantry and intellectual class have united under one ideology, which rejects the urban lifestyle in favour of the rural.*[NEWLINE]Whether good or ill will come of this, it is hard to say. For now, we shall have to endure.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_BULGARIA_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>*The upstart nations of the world cannot stand a free and strong Bulgaria. The men and women of this country are ready to march against them, even if it means their deaths*[NEWLINE]For honour. For glory!</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PROMOTION_UE_ORDEROFMERIT">
			<Text>Order Of Merit</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PROMOTION_UE_ORDEROFMERIT_HELP">
			<Text>Earn Science and Culture from Kills.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
